{"tid":1827786,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港膺全球最昂貴城市","createTime":"2020-01-17T08:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T09:02:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e790bafbaa0dff2af23524df5241a800220ea11","tid":1827786,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:30:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200117/VLUDTNFBFYCN4NY43622EJ5PIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200117%2FVLUDTNFBFYCN4NY43622EJ5PIQ%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyswCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=906e8d0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200117%2FVLUDTNFBFYCN4NY43622EJ5PIQ%2F&h=0aa08f29\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200117/VLUDTNFBFYCN4NY43622EJ5PIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港膺全球最昂貴城市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200117/large/1579192697_aafe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200117%2Flarge%2F1579192697_aafe.jpg&h=4b454be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港成為全球最昂貴的城市。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n瑞士寶盛首期《全球財富和高端生活報告》追蹤全球28個主要城市中20個消費項目，當中香港成為全球最昂貴的城市。瑞士寶盛私人銀行亞太區市場及財富管理方案部主管Rajesh Manwani指，香港的高端貨品及服務是荒謬地昂貴，因為香港在各項高端貨品中，包括高級餐飲、商務機票、女鞋等，處於全球第90個百分位數上。另外，香港在房地產、美容服務等方面的價格遠高於全球，因此成為最昂貴城市。"},{"pid":"bf145f51e0aee67bdc22ce826411c4da1416ed86","tid":1827786,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"January 17, 2020<br />\n紅磡:龍門冰室 x 香港人嘅冰室資源分享中心<br />\n12p 觀塘:和你宵<br />\n1p 新蒲崗和你lunch - 119遮打見<br />\n1p 長沙灣x荔枝角 手足和你Lunch<br />\n1p 黃竹坑和你Lunch<br />\n4p 北區醫院:醫護界街站<br />\n6p 大埔中學生集會<br />\n7p 石蔭和你寫<br />\n7p 油麻地:鼠年和你寫<br />\n7p 沙田:和你傾<br />\n9p 紅磡:「齊上齊落 不離不棄」<br />\n<br />\nRef :<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http